## Skill Discovery

I can help you find and install new skills for Russell.

### What I Can Do

| Action | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| **Search** | Find skills matching a symptom via web search |
| **Evaluate** | Assess skill safety, quality, compatibility |
| **Download** | Fetch skill to sandbox for review |
| **Install** | Install skill after approval |
| **Recommend** | Suggest skills for capability gaps |

